data.description: Welcome! This expansive 3 bedroom, 2 and -a-half-bath townhome is the perfect blend of style, convenience, and the comfort of Florida. Step inside and be greeted by the open and airy layout, perfect for modern living.    The well-appointed kitchen features all the essentials, while the adjoining living and dining areas provide an inviting space for relaxation and entertainment. Walk through the sliding doors to discover a serene completely screened patio, an ideal spot for enjoying the beautiful Florida weather.     The primary bedroom impresses with its en-suite bathroom, complete with a double vanity and walk-in shower. Two additional bedrooms provide versatility for guests, a home office, or your desired use.    This townhome doesn't just stop at its interior charm. With a one-car garage, a covered front porch, and a driveway for extra parking, you'll have plenty of space for all your needs.     Don't miss your chance to make this townhome yours!    Community Benefits: Water, internet, cable ,and landscaping are all included in the HOA    Experience a lifestyle of ease and comfort in this Ruskin gem.     **Special Financing Programs Available    We're thrilled to partner with our preferred lender, who offers financing programs designed to make your first home purchase even more accessible.      These programs can help with:  Closing Costs - Up to $10,000 in closing costs assistance    Down Payment - Finance up to the entire down payment    **These offers CAN be combined!
